comments: Hayward (CHA) brings his hands toward Irving (DAL) and marginal contact occurs as Hayward releases away to receive the pass.
Irving (DAL) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with Hayward's (CHA) arm.
Smith Jr. (CHA) and Kleber (DAL) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs prior to setting the pick.
Williams (CHA) establishes himself in Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Bullock (DAL) brings his arm toward Williams' (CHA) path and does not deliver illegal contact as he sets the screen.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) engages and disengages with Williams (CHA) and marginal contact occurs as Williams rolls to the basket.
Washington (CHA) bobbles the dribble without pinning it to his back, prior to releasing the pass to his teammate.
Doncic (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position and incidental contact occurs as he defends Washington (CHA) during the drive.
Hayward (CHA) establishes his left foot as his pivot and maintains it as he starts his dribble.
Klebler (DAL) commits a take foul on Mykhailiuk (CHA).
Kleber (DAL) firms up in Washington's (CHA) path and absorbs the incidental contact as Kleber sets the screen.
Doncic (DAL) establishes himself in Smith Jr.'s (CHA) path and his legs remain within the frame of his body as contact occurs, which he does not deliver.
Washington (CHA) legally contests Doncic's (DAL) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
